.shell powershell

## Reload whkd configuration
ctrl + alt + shift + o      : komorebic stop ; komorebic restore-windows ; komorebic start --whkd --masir
alt + n                     : Start-Process -WindowStyle Hidden rio.exe

## App shortcuts - these require shell to be pwsh / powershell
## The apps will be focused if open, or launched if not open
## alt + f                      : if ($wshell.AppActivate('Firefox') -eq $False) { start firefox }
## alt + b                      : if ($wshell.AppActivate('Chrome') -eq $False) { start chrome }

## Workspaces
alt + 1                     : komorebic focus-workspace 0
alt + 2                     : komorebic focus-workspace 1
alt + 3                     : komorebic focus-workspace 2
alt + 4                     : komorebic focus-workspace 3
alt + 5                     : komorebic focus-workspace 4
alt + 6                     : komorebic focus-workspace 5
alt + 7                     : komorebic focus-workspace 6
alt + 8                     : komorebic focus-workspace 7

## Cycle Workspace
alt + oem_comma             : komorebic cycle-workspace previous
alt + oem_period            : komorebic cycle-workspace next

## Manipulate Workspace
alt + shift + n             : komorebic new-workspace
alt + shift + w             : komorebic close-workspace

## Move windows across Workspaces
alt + shift + 1             : komorebic move-to-workspace 0
alt + shift + 2             : komorebic move-to-workspace 1
alt + shift + 3             : komorebic move-to-workspace 2
alt + shift + 4             : komorebic move-to-workspace 3
alt + shift + 5             : komorebic move-to-workspace 4
alt + shift + 6             : komorebic move-to-workspace 5
alt + shift + 7             : komorebic move-to-workspace 6
alt + shift + 8             : komorebic move-to-workspace 7

## Cycle move windows across Workspaces
alt + shift + oem_comma     : komorebic cycle-move-to-workspace previous
alt + shift + oem_period    : komorebic cycle-move-to-workspace next

## Focus windows
alt + vk_left               : komorebic focus left
alt + vk_down               : komorebic focus down
alt + vk_up                 : komorebic focus up
alt + vk_right              : komorebic focus right
alt + oem_4                 : komorebic cycle-focus previous
alt + oem_6                 : komorebic cycle-focus next

## Move windows
alt + shift + vk_left       : komorebic move left
alt + shift + vk_down       : komorebic move down
alt + shift + vk_up         : komorebic move up
alt + shift + vk_right      : komorebic move right
alt + shift + return        : komorebic promote
vk_LWIN + oem_4             : komorebic cycle-focus previous
vk_LWIN + oem_6             : komorebic cycle-focus next

## Resize
alt + oem_plus              : komorebic resize-axis horizontal increase
alt + oem_minus             : komorebic resize-axis horizontal decrease
alt + shift + oem_plus      : komorebic resize-axis vertical increase
alt + shift + oem_minus     : komorebic resize-axis vertical decrease

## Manipulate windows
alt + t                     : komorebic toggle-float
alt + f                     : komorebic toggle-monocle
alt + w                     : komorebic close
alt + m                     : komorebic minimize

## Window manager options
alt + shift + r             : komorebic unmanage ; komorebic manage

## Layouts
alt + x                     : komorebic flip-layout horizontal
alt + y                     : komorebic flip-layout vertical
alt + oem_5                 : komorebic cycle-layout next
alt + shift + oem_5         : komorebic cycle-layout previous
ctrl + alt + oem_5          : komorebic change-layout scrolling

## Stacking
ctrl + alt + left           : komorebic stack left
ctrl + alt + down           : komorebic stack down
ctrl + alt + up             : komorebic stack up
ctrl + alt + right          : komorebic stack right
alt + shift + oem_4         : komorebic cycle-stack previous
alt + shift + oem_6         : komorebic cycle-stack next
alt + oem_1                 : komorebic unstack
ctrl + alt + oem_1          : komorebic unstack-all

alt + s                     : yasbc toggle-widget launchpad --follow-mouse
